snippet.title: Earthlingo Gameplay Demo
snippet.description:
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1472136498
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.simify.earthlingo
MacOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1471614158
Windows and Linux: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1071240
Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/Earthlingo-2356645841259648

Currently Earthlingo teaches Japanese, French and English. It has 750 words across 8 levels. In the next few months I'll be releasing more game modes and vocabulary.
